了公司董事会的标准。据<em>路透社报道</em>，7.35 亿美元的和解金将通过所谓的“衍生诉讼”返还给特斯拉，这是特拉华州衡平法院有史以来判决的最大金额的赔偿金。</p><p>特斯拉辩称，股票期权是用来确保董事的激励措施与投资者的目标保持一致。特斯拉尚未对此事发表评论，但在法庭文件中表示，它同意和解以消除未来诉讼的风险。</p><p>特斯拉首席执行官埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 正在另外提起诉讼，为其 560 亿美元的薪酬方案辩护。它是由股东理查德·托内特（Richard Tornette） <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.bizjournals.com/sanjose/news/2019/09/23/judge-orders-tesla-board-to-face-trial-with.html">提出的</a>，他声称“人类历史上最大的补偿金”给予了马斯克，尽管他并不完全关注特斯拉。 2020 年，作为该计划的一部分，他收到了<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/teslas-texas-factory-has-produced-its-first-cybertruck-161840934.html">12 笔 7 亿美元付款中的第一笔</a>。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/tesla-directors-agree-to-return-735-million-following-claims-they-were-massively-overpaid-105506056.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/tesla-directors-agree-to-return-735-million-following-claims-they-were-massively-overpaid-105506056.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 258a76e3-16b1-49a9-bca7-d55733772d5a</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫·登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jul 2023 10:55:06 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689674115</ingested><modified> 2023-07-18T09:55:20+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[Company Legal & Law Matters]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="1920" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/095902a0-254a-11ee-baff-a734193e8db3" width="3000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1920" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/095902a0-254a-11ee-baff-a734193e8db3" width="3000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[FILE - A sign marks the entrance to the Tesla Gigafactory, Oct. 13, 2018, in Sparks, Nev. Tesla will get more than $330 million in tax breaks from Nevada to massively expand its vehicle battery facility east of Reno and add a new electric semi-truck factory. Approval on Thursday, March 2, 2023, from the Governor's Office of Economic Development came as Republican Gov. Joe Lombardo cited the benefit of jobs and the boost that Tesla's huge Gigafactory has given the local economy for almost a decade. (AP Photo/John Locher, File)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Tesla Expansion Nevada Taxes]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Tesla's 'Charge on Solar' lets Powerwall owners send excess energy to their EV]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/teslas-texas-factory-has-produced-its-first-cybertruck-161840934.html">特斯拉</a>推出了一项名为“<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.tesla.com/support/tesla-app/charge-on-solar">太阳能充电</a>”的功能，允许车主仅使用多余的太阳能来为电动汽车的电池充电。正如<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://techcrunch.com/2023/07/17/tesla-lets-owners-recharge-with-solar/"><em>TechCrunch</em></a>指出的那样，该汽车制造商于 5 月份开始测试该功能，但现在它已更广泛地提供给美国和加拿大的特斯拉客户。然而，可以访问该功能的人数可能仍然非常有限。首先，只有那些拥有较新特斯拉（2021 年及以后）并且还拥有 Powerwall 的人才能使用它。这是该公司的电池系统，用于存储太阳能电池板利用的太阳能。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/db445110-2546-11ee-affe-bd8d5e67861e" style="height:1051px;width:1536px;" alt="特斯拉新太阳能充电功能的屏幕截图。" data-uuid="90a24675-5ddd-308d-975b-681f6dd502d7"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">特斯拉</div></figure><p>要启用太阳能充电，用户需要启动特斯拉应用程序，选择该功能，然后进行设置。然后，他们会在功能设置中看到一个带有太阳图标的滑块，他们可以向左或向右拖动该滑块来设置充电限制。在到达太阳滑块之前，车辆将像往常一样通过太阳能和电网自行充电，确保用户有足够的电力到达他们需要的地方。但到达太阳滑块后，车辆只会使用多余的太阳能为自己充电。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>当处于风暴监视模式时，Powerwall 仍会优先存储备用能源或为其他设备充电，然后再分配任何多余的太阳能用于车辆充电。太阳能充电实际上只会使用多余的能量为电动汽车充电，这也是为什么担心电量不足的车主可以为其设置时间限制。当然，如果他们想绝对确保电池充满电，他们也可以调整充电限制，或者完全关闭太阳能充电。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/teslas-charge-on-solar-lets-powerwall-owners-send-excess-energy-to-their-ev-102018496.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/teslas-charge-on-solar-lets-powerwall-owners-send-excess-energy-to-their-ev-102018496.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 736d92ae-3551-4835-8ea6-2ade4cabfa6f</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jul 2023 10:20:18 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689672682</ingested><modified> 2023-07-18T09:31:39+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Solar Power]]></category><category><![CDATA[Renewable Energy & Energy Saving]]></category><category><![CDATA[Environment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Nature & Environment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="1021" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/ba618b30-2545-11ee-bff7-668c9526853b" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1021" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/ba618b30-2545-11ee-bff7-668c9526853b" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Tesla]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A house with solar panels on the roof. In front of the garage door is a red Tesla plugged into an outlet. White Powerwall units are visible on the outside wall of the garage.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Tesla]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[VanMoof e-bikes has declared bankruptcy]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/vanmoof-s4-x4-e-bikes-release-date-pricing-colors-110017301.html">电动自行车公司 VanMoof</a>已宣布其所有荷兰实体破产，并计划在“未来几周”内找到买家。与此同时，阿姆斯特丹法院撤销了暂停付款程序，并任命了两名受托人来监督可能的第三方资产出售，以理想地维持 VanMoof 的运作。这一消息是通过一封发给<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.reddit.com/r/vanmoofbicycle/comments/152g897/vanmoof_bankruptcy_statement_in_full/">荷兰员工的群发电子邮件</a>传出的，该电子邮件随后在 Reddit 上分享。</p><p> VanMoof 在宣布投资 1.28 亿美元并声称自己是“世界上资金最多的电动自行车公司”后不到两年就进入了破产程序。然而，麻烦已经酝酿了一段时间，据称其自行车销售和维修成本高于人们购买自行车的成本。荷兰金融机构<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://fd.nl/financiele-markten/1465594/vanmoof-is-te-goedkoop">FD 报告称</a>，2021 年 VanMoof 的毛利率损失为 1190 万欧元（1340 万美元），其中 800 万欧元（900 万美元）用于维修和更换。该公司在美国和台湾等地的国际实体不属于破产程序的一部分。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>范莫夫告诉员工，“没有资金支付长期工资”，并给了他们六周的通知期，预计他们将在这段时间内工作并收到最终付款。其中一部分时间是将目前正在使用的自行车返还给客户。 VanMoof 非常希望员工能够继续努力工作，他表示：“有必要保持坚强，继续完成自己需要做的工作。我们希望每个人都能继续努力，这样我们就能为这家美丽的公司创造一个美好的未来。”共同打造品牌。”</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/vanmoof-e-bikes-has-declared-bankruptcy-094041635.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/vanmoof-e-bikes-has-declared-bankruptcy-094041635.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> d57b4876-750f-4567-8ffd-fc25aeef6614</guid><dc:creator>萨拉·菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jul 2023 09:40:41 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689672167</ingested><modified> 2023-07-18T09:22:54+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Finance]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="1333" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-10/10806610-456f-11ed-bf5d-71f0d054f405" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1333" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-10/10806610-456f-11ed-bf5d-71f0d054f405" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Mat Smith/Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[VanMoof S5 first impressions]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[VanMoof S5 first impressions]]></media:title></media:content></item></channel></rss>